Catering
Find out who you can hire as a caterer for an event.
Rates
The Tavares  Pavilion has a variety of meeting rooms and event spaces available for your special day. Facilities can be booked up to 18 months in advance and are first-come-first-served. To secure the reservation, a deposit equal to 50% of the rental fee shall be paid to the City of Tavares upon the signing of the contract.
Simply Married
Don't have time for an elaborate ceremony, but still want a memorable wedding day? Choose Simply Married!
Floor Plans & Seating
The Tavares Pavilion on the Lake is comprised of two floors that include two grand ballrooms, meeting space and a 150 foot brick paved pier.
